title: Best of the Program | Guests: Janice Dean & Jedediah Bila | 12/13/21
description:
Fox News’ Janice Dean joins to discuss Chris Cuomo, his alleged insulting texts toward her, and her fight against the Cuomo family. Bill O’Reilly joins to discuss his tour with Donald Trump. Author Jedediah Bila joins to discuss the downfall of New York post-COVID.
